1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,225
=Episode 13=

3
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:05,640
I'm sorry.

4
00:01:06,119 --> 00:01:07,200
We did everything we could.

5
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:01,200
Tell me!

6
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,560
Was this your doing?

7
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,000
It wasn't me.

8
00:02:04,439 --> 00:02:05,040
Mr. Ye.

9
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:05,959
Mr. Ye, listen to me.

10
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:08,110
As soon as it happened,
I went to track down the driver.

11
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:08,879
We caught him.

12
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,359
Found him at Dongjiang Pier.

13
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,560
Do you know him?

14
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,520
Speak up.

15
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,840
Do you know me?

16
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,560
No. I really don't.

17
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,879
Tell the truth!

18
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,500
It wasn't me, really!

19
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,012
Someone paid me

20
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:25,919
to do it.

21
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:26,400
Who?

22
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:27,520
I don't know.

23
00:02:27,530 --> 00:02:29,080
The money was transferred from overseas.

24
00:02:29,110 --> 00:02:30,120
I don't know who sent it.

25
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,879
I checked already.

26
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:33,160
The payment did come
from an encrypted account abroad.

27
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,320
I'm still tracking it down.

28
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:34,800
Mr. Ye,

29
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,439
you might want to ask him

30
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,000
what he used to do for work.

31
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:38,840
Speak.

32
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:42,120
I used to drive a raw-materials
delivery truck

33
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,080
for Huaying Pharma.

34
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:46,800
I swear.

35
00:02:47,060 --> 00:02:48,300
I really don't know anything.

36
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:58,840
Get up!

37
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,039
Mr. Ye,

38
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,759
for safety reasons,

39
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:03,360
I suggest you leave Jinzhou first.

40
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,990
I've already made the arrangements.

41
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,639
Madam Li has already been killed.

42
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,840
What safety is there left?

43
00:03:10,220 --> 00:03:12,007
I'm staying here
until I find out the truth.

44
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:14,520
If Qin Gang is really behind this,

45
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,912
I'll make him pay with his life.

46
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,039
What do you plan to do?

47
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,600
I'll support you with everything I have.

48
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,280
I have my own rules.

49
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:23,919
If you truly want to help me,

50
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,120
then follow my rules.

51
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:27,719
Alright.

52
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:29,879
I'll do whatever you say.

53
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,639
I made osmanthus cakes for you today.

54
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,719
It's your favorite.

55
00:03:55,719 --> 00:03:56,280
Here.

56
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,520
Is it good?

57
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,360
(Madam Li.)

58
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,159
(Rest assured.)

59
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:11,560
(I will catch the murderer)

60
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,719
(and avenge you.)

61
00:04:30,837 --> 00:04:32,846
(Anyone who dares hurt my family)

62
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:36,720
(will pay the price.)

63
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,000
Let's go inside and take a look.

64
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,560
We shouldn't hold it in.

65
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:45,279
Alright.

66
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,279
You all haven't eaten yet, right?

67
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,519
I'll go cook.

68
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,079
Chen.

69
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:00,040
Are you okay?

70
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:03,639
I'm fine.

71
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:07,319
Life still has to go on.

72
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,879
I've figured it out.

73
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:12,660
Even if I cried my heart out,
Madam Li wouldn't come back.

74
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:14,399
For her sake,

75
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,839
and for this family,

76
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,079
I'll keep going.

77
00:05:21,330 --> 00:05:22,319
You scared me to death.

78
00:05:23,079 --> 00:05:24,319
That's the right way to think.

79
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:28,639
I'll make something.

80
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,240
Dinner will be ready soon.

81
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,360
I'll keep you company.

82
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,990
What are you doing here?

83
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,360
Ye Chen.

84
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:30,000
You're here, Mr. Qin?

85
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:32,160
Ye Chen,

86
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:35,639
I know you must suspect me right now.

87
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:37,160
That's understandable.

88
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,279
It's fine.

89
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,680
But

90
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:42,160
let me tell you something.

91
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:45,079
I, Qin Gang, have my own principles.

92
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:46,639
I would never involve someone's family.

93
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:50,980
You're overthinking it.

94
00:06:52,150 --> 00:06:53,160
It was just an accident.

95
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,162
Why would I suspect you, Mr. Qin?

96
00:06:59,160 --> 00:06:59,759
Ms. Qin,

97
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,399
does your challenge still stand?

98
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,319
I accept it.

99
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:10,639
Really?

100
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,500
Okay, original plan.

101
00:07:12,510 --> 00:07:14,050
Three days from now, we meet at the gym

102
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:14,990
and have a proper match.

103
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:24,399
Why did you agree to fight her?

104
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,279
No reason.

105
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,800
I just felt like having a fight.

106
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,639
You think I don't know you?

107
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,079
Tell me the truth.

108
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,360
What are you really planning?

109
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:36,839
Churan,

110
00:07:38,439 --> 00:07:39,279
there are some things

111
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,360
I can't tell you right now.

112
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:43,120
But I promise nothing will happen to us.

113
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,519
Trust me.

114
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:50,240
Mr. Hong,

115
00:07:51,375 --> 00:07:52,639
can you teach me or not?

116
00:07:53,210 --> 00:07:54,489
Just give me a straight answer.

117
00:07:57,530 --> 00:07:58,879
I'm not trying to discourage you,

118
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,959
but martial arts

119
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,480
take years of steady practice.

120
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:05,759
I know Qin Aoxue.

121
00:08:06,100 --> 00:08:07,980
She's been a martial arts fanatic
since she was little.

122
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,759
All she does every day is train.

123
00:08:10,439 --> 00:08:11,319
Back then,

124
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,825
she even came to learn from me.

125
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:15,759
(Ye Chen)
Now her skills are no joke.

126
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,560
In all of Jinzhou,

127
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,760
there are only a few people
who can defeat her.

128
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:22,279
Chen,

129
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,800
listen to my advice.

130
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,160
There's no need for you to fight her.

131
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,199
But I must fight!

132
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,170
Actually, I also trained in martial arts
when I was young.

133
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,279
But I fell very ill
and forgot everything.

134
00:08:36,199 --> 00:08:37,400
If I could remember it again,

135
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,919
maybe I'd stand a chance.

136
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,080
But...

137
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,320
Mr. Hong, please teach me.

138
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,279
I have to remember it
as soon as possible.

139
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,519
Only by becoming stronger

140
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,120
can I protect the people
I care about most.

141
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:56,759
Aoxue,

142
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:59,639
I want to discuss something with you.

143
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:02,600
How about we cancel

144
00:09:02,879 --> 00:09:03,679
this match?

145
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:05,840
Why?

146
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,440
Come here.

147
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:09,799
I just feel

148
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,840
that Ye Chen isn't trustworthy.

149
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:20,200
I think

150
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,639
he might use some dirty tricks

151
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,679
to set you up.

152
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,240
You don't think I can beat him, do you?

153
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,559
Not exactly...

154
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:28,519
But look at you now...

155
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:29,639
Doesn't that say it all?

156
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,700
I'm going back to training.

157
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,680
I still can't remember anything.

158
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:48,279
Take it easy, Chen.

159
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:50,320
Mr. Hong,

160
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:51,840
hit me.

161
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,440
What?

162
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,360
Hit me hard.

163
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:56,200
You... You're not joking, are you?

164
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:57,600
Here I go!

165
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,639
Are you okay?

166
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:01,960
I'm fine.

167
00:10:02,570 --> 00:10:02,960
Come on.

168
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,900
Why do you keep aiming for my stomach?

169
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,840
I didn't hit your stomach now, did I?

170
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,679
Again!

171
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:29,290
Do you really have
to torture yourself like this?

172
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,960
They're just superficial wounds.

173
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,559
I'm fine.

174
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,290
Serves you right.

175
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:38,759
Churan,

176
00:10:40,639 --> 00:10:41,480
I'm really fine.

177
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:43,240
But I have to get my memory back.

178
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,080
I just want to know

179
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:46,879
who I really am.

180
00:10:58,410 --> 00:11:00,799
That useless Ye Chen
actually dares challenge your sister?

181
00:11:01,039 --> 00:11:02,080
He must have a death wish.

182
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:03,480
Have Aoxue

183
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,759
beat him up properly.

184
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:05,919
What's it got to do with you?

185
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:13,159
Aodong...

186
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,120
You've been tired all day.

187
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,440
Let me give you a massage.

188
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:18,759
How many times have I told you?

189
00:11:18,759 --> 00:11:20,080
I'm not interested in you.

190
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,320
Got it?

191
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:21,879
Mm-hmm.

192
00:11:22,159 --> 00:11:23,360
Why are you acting so wronged?

193
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:28,970
What are you staring at?

194
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:30,440
Your forehead is full,

195
00:11:30,725 --> 00:11:32,147
your jawline broad and square.

196
00:11:32,512 --> 00:11:34,512
Young man,

197
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:36,437
your destiny is one of great nobility.

198
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,360
You don't say.

199
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:40,799
However...

200
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:42,159
your glabella is darkening.

201
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:43,919
An ominous aura has appeared.

202
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:45,799
Your fate has taken a turn
for the worse.

203
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:47,360
Disaster is approaching.

204
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,320
Such a pity...

205
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,159
Hey, wait a minute.

206
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:51,159
Who are you?

207
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,720
Young man, calm your anger.

208
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,440
I am Yu Jinghai.

209
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:57,080
Wait, you...

210
00:11:57,530 --> 00:12:00,120
You wouldn't happen to be Master Yu
from Xuanji Hall, would you?

211
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:04,000
This man is practically a living legend!

212
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,080
Master Yu,

213
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,279
please, have a seat.

214
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:07,960
You must help

215
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,399
take a careful look

216
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:11,000
at Aodong.

217
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:12,639
Very well.

218
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,279
I'll take a look

219
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,960
for you.

220
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,840
Aodong, he is a living legend.

221
00:12:20,412 --> 00:12:20,692
Come,

222
00:12:20,799 --> 00:12:22,039
let Master Yu examine you.

223
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:23,663
Let's have a good look.

224
00:12:50,399 --> 00:12:51,200
I see it clearly now.

225
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,559
Your destiny has taken a turn.

226
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:53,900
I see a petty villain in your fate.

227
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:55,240
As the saying goes,

228
00:12:55,639 --> 00:12:56,639
you've run into bad luck.

229
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:57,679
Master Yu,

230
00:12:57,879 --> 00:13:01,120
please help Aodong
dispel the evil and avert the disaster.

231
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,279
Bad luck indeed...

232
00:13:06,399 --> 00:13:06,919
You...

233
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:07,600
Wait, this is...

234
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,200
That's only right, isn't it?

235
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:09,919
As it should be.

236
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,399
Alright then.

237
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:12,360
Mr. Qin,

238
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,960
you stand for righteousness.

239
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,480
Yes.

240
00:13:15,639 --> 00:13:18,039
And I stand for compassion.

241
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:18,960
Since fate

242
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:23,320
has brought us together...

243
00:13:23,519 --> 00:13:24,559
Master...

244
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,120
Master...

245
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:26,900
He's a true master!

246
00:13:27,159 --> 00:13:27,879
Don't worry.

247
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,000
You won't die anytime soon.

248
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,120
What?

249
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:34,519
Because a noble person
has taken the disaster on your behalf.

250
00:13:35,639 --> 00:13:36,240
Master, I...

251
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,240
I want to ask.

252
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:37,679
Where...

253
00:13:37,679 --> 00:13:39,039
is the... noble person?

254
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,120
The noble person

255
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,759
is far in the distance,

256
00:13:43,650 --> 00:13:44,759
yet right before your eyes.

257
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,039
It's her?

258
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,799
She has a full face

259
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,120
and a prominent nose bridge.

260
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:54,840
A face that brings good fortune
to her husband.

261
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,639
Good fortune for the husband?

262
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:56,420
- Good...
- Fortune.

263
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:58,100
- Good fortune?
- Yes, good fortune.

264
00:13:58,799 --> 00:13:59,679
Good fortune.

265
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,519
Look at the two of you.

266
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:06,559
You two are a match made in heaven.

267
00:14:06,737 --> 00:14:07,950
A match made in heaven?

268
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:08,799
Really?

269
00:14:10,279 --> 00:14:11,000
However,

270
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,919
a fortunate face alone

271
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:15,080
can't solve the root of the problem.

272
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,080
So tomorrow,

273
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:21,200
at noon,
when the Yang energy is strongest,

274
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:24,533
I'll go to your residence
and conduct a feng shui inspection.

275
00:14:24,533 --> 00:14:26,212
I want to see

276
00:14:26,212 --> 00:14:27,550
what kind of evil force

277
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:28,399
dares

278
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:30,000
to be so unruly.

279
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:30,879
That's all.

280
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,120
Let us walk you out.

281
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:32,919
- No need.
- Master Yu!

282
00:14:32,919 --> 00:14:33,600
We'll see you out.

283
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,639
Master Yu, please take care.

284
00:14:35,639 --> 00:14:36,200
Master...

285
00:14:40,399 --> 00:14:42,200
Bless us please, Master.

286
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,279
Master Yu.

287
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,840
Don't worry. The amount is correct.

288
00:14:59,399 --> 00:14:59,919
I will

289
00:15:00,279 --> 00:15:01,200
Ieave it to you then.

290
00:15:26,587 --> 00:15:29,075
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

291
00:15:29,162 --> 00:15:32,915
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

292
00:15:33,375 --> 00:15:38,312
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

293
00:15:38,475 --> 00:15:40,762
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

294
00:15:41,075 --> 00:15:43,755
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

295
00:15:44,825 --> 00:15:47,450
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

296
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:50,762
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

297
00:15:50,962 --> 00:15:54,012
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

298
00:15:54,125 --> 00:15:57,087
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

299
00:15:57,355 --> 00:16:00,512
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

300
00:16:00,737 --> 00:16:04,487
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

301
00:16:04,487 --> 00:16:07,350
♪I belong to no one♪

302
00:16:07,412 --> 00:16:10,862
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

303
00:16:10,862 --> 00:16:13,537
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

304
00:16:13,537 --> 00:16:19,875
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
